### post test
//@name postTest
POST https://{{host}}/post
User-Agent: curl/7.47.0
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "{{nick}}",
  "age": 42,
  "uuid": "{{$uuid}}",
  "demo": "hi` morning"
