//@name graphqlSimple
GRAPHQL https://httpbin.org/post

query {
    ip
}

### GraphQL demo with variables
//@name graphqlDemo
GRAPHQL https://httpbin.org/post

query {
    ip
}

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "hi` morning"
}
